      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Whoso findeth a wife — A good wife; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "one that deserves the name, and performs the duty of that relation. Thus Houbigant interprets it after many of the versions: see ",
